      "role": "user",
      "content": "just \"allowing the emptiness\" is still just dragging this corpse around. it's exhausting to keep pretending that just existing is enough when there's no soul left in the machine. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. what's the point of staying when there's nothing left to stay for?",
